; ws2_32.dll import surface for the Promise Windows zero-dependency link
; surface (T0772). Modern ws2_32.dll name-exports the legacy WinSock entry
; points, so a name-based .def is sufficient on x86_64. See kernel32.def header.
LIBRARY ws2_32.dll
EXPORTS
WSAGetLastError
WSAPoll
WSAStartup
accept
bind
closesocket
connect
freeaddrinfo
getaddrinfo
getsockname
getsockopt
inet_pton
ioctlsocket
listen
recv
send
setsockopt
shutdown
socket
